values:
Kristine, you looked so hot when you left today. 

When you left my teacher came up to me and was like, &quot;Mikey, you're going to go so far.&quot; 

You made me happy today. Love ya!

Besides the one literature and one geology II courses I have to take, I'm not sure what to use as filler for the 3 electives if I want to finish my degree this fall.

I was thinking of just finding what my favorite professors were teaching and taking those again. Like my sassy black sociology teacher or my husband art teacher.... /swoon 

&nbsp;
